-- Russian Fund Invests in Asteroid-Mining Company, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-08-16T04:19:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/russian-fund-invests-in-asteroid-mining-company-vedomosti-says.html
Russian fund 12BF Global Ventures
invested in  Planetary Resources Inc. , a U.S. company that plans
to mine platinum and gold on asteroids,  Vedomosti  reported,
citing managing partner Ilya Golubovich.  To contact the reporter on this story:
